text.text:
The mosque is easy to access, it is on the edge of the main road (Jalan Raya Ciamis Banjar), close to Banjar station. For those who are traveling, it is suitable for stopping to pray or rest. The main room is quite spacious. The yard is large, you can park a car or motorbike. Motorbike parking costs Rp. 2,000,-
After the Isha prayer (19.18) the gate on the right was closed and the mosque door was also closed, the lights were turned off.
There are many stalls around the mosque for those who want to have a snack or quench their thirst.
Cleanliness of toilets & ablution areas needs to be improved. There is an infaq box for cleanliness but the toilet is not comfortable to use. Mosque carpets should also be washed regularly so that prayer is more comfortable, especially when prostrating ☺️

6/16/2023

originalText.text:
Masjidnya mudah diakses, ada di tepi jalan besar (Jalan Raya Ciamis Banjar), dekat dengan stasiun Banjar. Buat yang sedang dalam perjalanan, cocok buat menepi sholat atau istirahat. Ruang utama cukup luas. Halamannya luas, bisa untuk parkir mobil atau motor. Parkir motor dikenakan infaq Rp2.000,-
Habis sholat Isya (jam 19.18) pintu gerbang yg sebelah kanan sudah ditutup dan pintu masjid juga ditutup, lampunya sudah dimatikan.
Di sekitar masjid banyak warung buat yg mau jajan atau melepas dahaga.
Kebersihan toilet & tempat wudhu perlu ditingkatkan. Ada kotak infaq untuk kebersihan tapi toiletnya kurang nyaman digunakan. Karpet mesjidnya juga sebaiknya dicuci secara berkala ya agar sholatnya lebih nyaman, apalagi pas sujud ☺️

16/6/2023

text.text:
Tourists who are expected to arrive in Pangandaran in the morning will often stop at this mosque for morning prayers. Large buses and private vehicles also fill the parking area, some even parking on the side of the road.
The coffee and snack shops opened at dawn and were busy serving customers.

originalText.text:
Wisatawan yg diperkirakan akan sampai ke Pangandaran pagi hari lebih banyak mampir di masjid ini utk sholat subuh. Bus2 besar dan jg kendaraan pribadi memenuhi area parkir bahkan sebagian parkir di pinggir jalan.
Warung2 kopi dan jajanan sudah buka subuh dan ramai melayani pembeli.

text.text: The mosque is clean, the parking area is spacious enough for lots of cars and motorbikes. The ablution place for men is next to the mosque, while for women it is in the corner next to it. There are many canteens here, so it is also suitable as a place to rest. After prayer you can eat or drink. The location is in the city, easy to reach. Enjoy!

originalText.text: Masjidnya bersih, parkirannya luas bisa untuk banyak mobil dan motor. Tempat wudhu untuk laki-laki ada di samping masjid sedangkan untuk perempuan ada di pojok sebelahnya. Ada banyak kantin disini, jadi cocok juga untuk tempat istirahat. Setelah sholat bisa makan atau minum. Lokasi ada di kota, mudh di jangkau. Enjoy!
